\n佢搵返你？"},{"pid":"2bcff1b9014f3a9f13ff9d2a5666f6e89da56f4a","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左手成年<br />\n近排開始又拖拉過 唔知可以點向前/離開</blockquote><br />\n嗰年都有傾計？</blockquote><br />\n最近一兩個月先傾番計</blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢"},{"pid":"44526986843b51437776a3abb615ea5a7f4b7b7d","tid":109183,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:35:22.000Z","msg":"不過我肯等 等一生都等"},{"pid":"56b5964af81e56849d84e1c6a25f74585a7790f1","tid":109183,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:49:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過我肯等 等一生都等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾個限期自己 <br />\n真係鍾意你唔會要你等咁耐<br />\n呢個世界無童話"},{"pid":"1811a0d94bc2169865a26bfb4a51c8c1c653b1ff","tid":109183,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:49:28.000Z","msg":"等一個不會回頭的人"},{"pid":"816c9de781563729a04638eda688ac3553284b91","tid":109183,"uid":82168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"係fb ig見到舊同學以前好閃講到幾愛咁<br />\n分手兩 三個月後就有第二個<br />\n已經唔相信愛情可以last到幾耐"},{"pid":"1bda47d1ef25c747044b2124aef495d55e7b2c1e","tid":109183,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:52:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左手成年<br />\n近排開始又拖拉過 唔知可以點向前/離開</blockquote><br />\n嗰年都有傾計？</blockquote><br />\n最近一兩個月先傾番計</blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？"},{"pid":"34ae71371134703bebf6ad222845a42d6db9f87d","tid":109183,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:53:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手一年，依家仲等緊。。。</blockquote><br />\n唔撚駛等啦<br />\n比機會第二個啦"},{"pid":"f958b971fbf0ef9ed3a8c38303831ea4cdda4046","tid":109183,"uid":63869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:54:44.000Z","msg":"4年<br />\n最尾做返朋友 但心入面好憎佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6742b77561bd9cb130edd1b45f7922ddff2d39","tid":109183,"uid":20898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T07:54:56.000Z","msg":"請等候<br />\n要你等15分鐘都唔想等<br />\n更何況，等1年"},{"pid":"93a1e1207e5de2d4086a19c02d6b253907f777c8","tid":109183,"uid":41756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T10:05:41.000Z","msg":"我理性同自己講唔好等，但過左8個半月，每次經過拍拖去過嘅地方時一定會諗起同佢嘅回憶，特別係頭一年果d地方。<br />\n<br />\n佢已經俾其他仔溝緊，好似幾受。我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e6bb65cf2c7fc767de8c29a1f3864557b61d142","tid":109183,"uid":21064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T16:33:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我理性同自己講唔好等，但過左8個半月，每次經過拍拖去過嘅地方時一定會諗起同佢嘅回憶，特別係頭一年果d地方。<br />\n<br />\n佢已經俾其他仔溝緊，好似幾受。我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n搵另一個 <br />\n利申 做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae14cf8769d325dc844131e405850018fb387b70","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:10:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>以前等過5年<br />\nBTW 一切都會好的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇一齊翻？</blockquote><br />\n無，當初係佢飛我，佢話已經對我好厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁你點樣放棄等佢？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無架，等時間慢慢過囉<br />\n每晚都不停FF</blockquote><br />\n好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係好撚辛苦，晚晚訓唔著，不停FF，不停睇關於佢既所有野，一諗起就喊<br />\n依家諗起佢個心都仲會那住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我食唔落野、又訓唔著"},{"pid":"aa9d8eadb3f5687bf9e9b7670fcfc5e7de6f22bd","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:10:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔知。佢咩都封曬我。但我仲等緊佢。好傻。明知已經無可能。但係都放唔低。而且希望希一日可以從重黎過</blockquote><br />\n我明，佢都封左我，但又未封得曬咁lor"},{"pid":"512f159fd9d4511d4ca4249fe52a7f7a716eb259","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:11:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一年半<br />\n由人哋有仔等到分手斷尾<br />\n唔敢出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n單戀？"},{"pid":"11b5e1eaa3c2c09ce94b5a82c6d718029b390265","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手成年<br />\n近排開始又拖拉過 唔知可以點向前/離開</blockquote><br />\n我都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b002ce49afbcdbeeec47e5400a8a4722308d44db","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:12:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想知分手前封左我<br />\n<br />\n分手後一星期又解番係乜玩法<br />\n<br />\n明明帽左我兩年 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似我已經問過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b661e0bfd747ce10ca47a1885b799e8cb98e2089","tid":109183,"uid":27037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T20:13:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我理性同自己講唔好等，但過左8個半月，每次經過拍拖去過嘅地方時一定會諗起同佢嘅回憶，特別係頭一年果d地方。<br />\n<br />\n佢已經俾其他仔溝緊，好似幾受。我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我同佢去過嘅地方都會諗起佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3081b40fa4b5157755fc4caad72e37adaad6e105","tid":109183,"uid":81657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T22:30:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>[quote]我理性同自己講唔好等，但過左8個半月，每次經過拍拖去過嘅地方時一定會諗起同佢嘅回憶，特別係頭一年果d地方。<br />\n<br />\n佢已經俾其他仔溝緊，好似幾受。我可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係好難受，我ex已極速識左第2個，而我繼續失眠到天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1246c742d67a5f48575546c08e716d23904bc489","tid":109183,"uid":51108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-07T23:52:30.000Z","msg":"唔敢講話好明白你嘅感受<br />\n不過當年我都被人飛過<br />\n佢好狠咁cut off晒我同佢嘅所有嘢<br />\n<br />\nanyways, 好似之前一位巴絲打話齋<br />\n一切都會好的<br />\n<br />\n同埋當年朋友同我講過一句 &ldquo;你下一個會更好&rdquo;<br />\n當年聽到呢句好難受，但原來係真嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n加油，time to move on<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd181497401abddb03110d6e26757acaf189214","tid":109183,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:04:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想知分手前封左我<br />\n<br />\n分手後一星期又解番係乜玩法<br />\n<br />\n明明帽左我兩年 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好似我已經問過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都唔係好明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係解翻約左我見一次，不過係去佢工作地方買野，但我覺得佢冇咁低賤為左做我生意所以約出黎，始終太危險同佢仲有朋友係度<br />\n<br />\n我買完野仲肯行開同我傾幾句 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n究竟想點啊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd51ab732f227a6375520011f017f49f4472ee74","tid":109183,"uid":56682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:43:32.000Z","msg":"我仲好卦住佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唯有控制住自己。<br />\n<br />\n唔去了解佢近況。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2bbe54b94d52148b50a6bf5b372471ad6a13a6e","tid":109183,"uid":77803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T00:51:36.000Z","msg":"分左手，傾計果啲完全變晒朋友mode，但係我仲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39d91a7102545fac5362fc3b62477823db66f497","tid":109183,"uid":23552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:07:21.000Z","msg":"一世"},{"pid":"73e54da86916dad6a13d1d57415328beceafd114","tid":109183,"uid":75753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:07:46.000Z","msg":"女朋友等左我5年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 終於都一齊翻"},{"pid":"ece147959e895434b51047005bc3b779ab44b72e","tid":109183,"uid":53235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:53:21.000Z","msg":"傳說<br />\n初戀好難修成正果<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以單戀左兩年半到佢有另一半就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7013129627efd84dda376a417bbd3592abf88a","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T01:58:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>分左手成年<br />\n近排開始又拖拉過 唔知可以點向前/離開</blockquote><br />\n嗰年都有傾計？</blockquote><br />\n最近一兩個月先傾番計</blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim"},{"pid":"ccc6ddf943be4185c4bc87fe28412169f692482a","tid":109183,"uid":74560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"等到花兒都謝了"},{"pid":"286554b2ba60f145d7f77b30d74518b7afeff926","tid":109183,"uid":2411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T02:52:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我仲好卦住佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家唯有控制住自己