 />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊"},{"pid":"ca9097f3068d5df75af4d982c6771bbe14d0951a","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:45:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n嗰年都有傾計？</blockquote><br />\n最近一兩個月先傾番計</blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊</blockquote><br />\n我無 但唔知佢有冇 無問過"},{"pid":"68a239bd9c9b400739106aebf5dfeb147513f9d9","tid":109183,"uid":21202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T04:55:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n最近一兩個月先傾番計</blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊</blockquote><br />\n我無 但唔知佢有冇 無問過</blockquote><br />\n但而咖關係係融洽？"},{"pid":"2be648c6fd792f8ab78df7b1b4d973a3fd2634af","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:23:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n佢搵返你？</blockquote><br />\n我搵番佢</blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊</blockquote><br />\n我無 但唔知佢有冇 無問過</blockquote><br />\n但而咖關係係融洽？</blockquote><br />\n關係 融唔融洽好難講<br />\n只可以講 會一齊出街 佢會搵我 我會搵佢"},{"pid":"d233a9e58a923c168a363ecc3d9464e1616c49d8","tid":109183,"uid":83350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:42:19.000Z","msg":"等乜鳩丫 傻西"},{"pid":"f4137a82a92e992ba425ce7c544e2b42fc212610","tid":109183,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:54:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同佢講去自殺，等咗15分鐘，佢都無理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n臨郁手跟住自己喺度諗，究竟呢個女人係咪真係值得我咁做？唔值。<br />\n我冇on whatsapp24小時之後佢先開始瘋狂打比我打咗200幾次，但我知道呢個只係出於人性，而唔再係愛情</blockquote><br />\n垃圾俾我都唔理你"},{"pid":"2de17463c36ba44351e0e49322a20ee2b80cf55c","tid":109183,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T06:55:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>第四年<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我係呢一年見佢身邊好多女仔，個心好痛<br />\n我好想同番佢一齊</blockquote><br />\n你係我ex?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57398595e7bcf920d7b213ff47735b3fefb3dea9","tid":109183,"uid":14217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T07:51:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過我肯等 等一生都等</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾個限期自己 <br />\n真係鍾意你唔會要你等咁耐<br />\n呢個世界無童話</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n時日無多 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f5e0d20d83dad2aeefb43c8e8ee14766e71ff93","tid":109183,"uid":8264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:31:09.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0af793ed31e64da9bbb1d8ab8574f9ebcd4bf088","tid":109183,"uid":47391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T08:58:54.000Z","msg":"差唔多一年，知冇可能，唔想等，好辛苦，但對所有人都失去興趣，算唔算等<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416e760e86a822979956f59528bcaf98c9f59b34","tid":109183,"uid":54895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T14:10:08.000Z","msg":"人地唔中意你呀 你等極都冇人會可憐你<br />\n我都唔想等了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae918f7e957d115a91783d5bf10f4a11f48fd36","tid":109183,"uid":39570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T15:11:20.000Z","msg":"今年第五年<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ccf8732e07c39daae3cf769dce185fc9f8b9c9","tid":109183,"uid":31624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201