面，走唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 住左4年 好痛"},{"pid":"93085044c6363bf7f185d7a87046c7c66cc3d361","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:43:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊</blockquote><br />\n我無 但唔知佢有冇 無問過</blockquote><br />\n但而咖關係係融洽？</blockquote><br />\n關係 融唔融洽好難講<br />\n只可以講 會一齊出街 佢會搵我 我會搵佢</blockquote><br />\n成功在望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n睇落就唔係 唔知佢係咪搵我攝時間"},{"pid":"67ace4aaa92cdd96a4c604bea4f240d08966a60d","tid":109183,"uid":67418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:44:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n佢都肯同你傾？</blockquote><br />\n肯 仲出埋街tim</blockquote><br />\n但呢一年大家有冇同過其他人一齊</blockquote><br />\n我無 但唔知佢有冇 無問過</blockquote><br />\n但而咖關係係融洽？</blockquote><br />\n關係 融唔融洽好難講<br />\n只可以講 會一齊出街 佢會搵我 我會搵佢</blockquote><br />\n唉<br />\n我都想可以返去以前</blockquote><br />\n有時反而一齊番都唔係好事<br />\n至少我而家越來抗拒佢"},{"pid":"067c3440463994db58661ec85d0c6278f8bdd437","tid":109183,"uid":53769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:45:14.000Z","msg":"問題係等有用嗎"},{"pid":"96c6cdf1e70511e5ed719942370030f44a194078","tid":109183,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T17:53:56.000Z","msg":"心入面冇諗住要等幾耐/等唔等 只係心入面愛佢<br />\n開始覺得一切隨緣 其實佢都咁講<br />\n可能佢有男仔追都未定"},{"pid":"e4a26db019ad0817b9fadbf3a61d93bc2e2ab1f8","tid":109183,"uid":63001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T19:01:23.000Z","msg":"讀書時曾經單戀三年 但畢業後冇晒聯絡冇晒消息<br />\n途中拍過幾次拖但有時都會諗起佢<br />\n畢業後斷左聯絡三年 有日係m記撞到佢<br />\n同佢相視而笑揮個手之後我就走左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\"